item.title: FFM podcast finale: Winners, Losers and Lessons. Truworths, Textainer stand up; Implats, Pick n Pay hold the floor
item.description: In the dynamic world of fantasy fund management, where the thrills of the trading floor meet the strategic battlefields of a game board, a remarkable journey has come to a close. After 27 intense weeks of sharp moves, unforeseen market twirls, and astute stock selections, the Fantasy Fund Manager podcast stands as a testament to the spirited competition and financial education it has stirred among its participants... item.title: S4 E13 - Parenting Hell
item.description:
This week seems a little glum, Ben is still not having a good time with his health, however Will brings some cracking stories and experiences of just how difficult it can be being a Dad!

We've got some big games being covered this week, with Arsenal drubbing Sheffield Utd, Manchester City exposing all the issues going on at the red half of Manchester and all the rest of the weeks Premier League games... Feed: https://feeds.acast.com/public/shows/639c8ce16bb5ca00104d60b5
